      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple. i've done the therapy, i've talked to people, i've tried all the \"healthy\" things. nothing works. it's like a glitch in my life. no matter what i do, the outcome is always the same. i'm just exhausted by the repetition. it feels like the loop is the only thing that's actually real.",
